params.revisedPrompt: Imagine an extraterrestrial creature, with soft, luminescent skin in hues of royal blue and violet. This alien has multiple octopus-like appendages and large, round eyes that radiate a soft, yellow glow. This otherworldly entity is expertly riding a robust wave, showcasing its skill and balance. The wave, with its immense power and curling form, is crashing against the backdrop of a strange, alien sunset. The sky brims with gradients of orange and pink, dotted with alien planets hanging low on the horizon, casting peculiar shadows on the turbulent sea below.
